    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Any of the adjustable screws, usually in sets of four, in the rim of watch balance wheels used to bring the watch to time.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
